WEBVTT

00:05.038 --> 00:08.041
Color is an effective communication tool.

00:08.641 --> 00:11.644
It alerts us to important information.

00:13.146 --> 00:16.149
Can evoke emotion and mood

00:16.383 --> 00:19.386
and can draw attention to a focal point.

00:21.421 --> 00:23.656
When used correctly, color can help us

00:23.656 --> 00:26.793
in creating engaging and impactful presentations.

00:28.228 --> 00:31.431
So how do we know which color combinations are successful

00:31.865 --> 00:34.868
and which ones aren't?

00:36.770 --> 00:38.538
This course has been designed

00:38.571 --> 00:40.407
to help you choose harmonious colors

00:40.440 --> 00:43.443
that will elevate your presentation engagement.

00:44.144 --> 00:47.147
We'll be covering basics of color theory,

00:47.347 --> 00:50.283
what a color wheel is and how to use it,

00:50.417 --> 00:52.852
and exploring tools that can help you consistently

00:52.852 --> 00:55.288
create winning color combinations.
